I have an ad that is not showing any activity yet, it was completed at least 4 days ago

Let's try to figure out why your ad isn't showing any activity. Could you please check the following details for me?
1. **Campaign Start Date**: Make sure the campaign start date is set correctly in the ad manager, as it operates in PST/military time.
2. **Bidding Type**: Verify that your bidding type is set up correctly.
3. **Targeting or Budget Settings**: Double-check your targeting and budget settings to ensure they align with your campaign goals.
4. **Recent Changes**: Have there been any changes made to the campaign in the last 72 hours?
Once you've reviewed these factors, let me know if you need further assistance!

Thanks for checking those details. Since everything seems to be in order, it might be a good idea to give it a bit more time, as sometimes the system needs additional time to gather data and optimize performance. If the issue persists, I recommend reaching out to our support team for further assistance. You can email them at adsupport@newsbreak.com with your campaign details.
